H0.text: Teeth serve the same function as the horny ridges on the jaws for turtles.

H1.text: Skin serves the same function as the horny ridges on turtles' jaws.

H2.text: Taste buds are the function that the horny ridges on the jaws serve in turtles.

H3.text: Hairs are the horny ridges on the jaws that serve the same function as they do for turtles.
